body.description: Nature's Bounty Optimal Solutions Women’s Multivitamin Gummies offers a unique formula — created for women— to provide your body with over 10 key nutrients every day in a delicious raspberry and mixed berry flavored gummy. Nature's Bounty Optimal Solutions Women’s Multivitamin Gummies provide you with the vital nutrients to support a healthy and beautiful body. (1) Each daily serving provides your body with antioxidant Vitamins E and C, Calcium for bone health and Vitamin D for immune health. (1) This daily vitamin supplements also offers 50 mg of Collagen per serving. Other key nutrients, like B Vitamins, provide cellular energy support by helping convert food into energy. (1) This multi vitamin and mineral supplement plus collagen has no artificial flavors or sweeteners. Adults can take two raspberry-flavored gummies per day, preferably with a meal. Each bottle of Nature's Bounty Optimal Solutions Women's Multivitamin Gummies contains 140 delicious raspberry flavored gummies.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars It growss my hair and nails like crazy
reviews.reviewText: I’ve never used vitamins before and I’m 28 .. I wanted something simple that had everything my body needed or most…I actually bought my first after seeing the TikTok girlies raving about it and it did not disappoint I’ve never been able to grow out my nails it takes forever and I can honestly say this works for me .. I recommend it to my mom and she did complain of being nauseous after using it so idk if it’s gonna work for everybody but I got no side effects ..I ensure to take it everyday but I don’t have a specific time it’s whenever I remember … I usually eat half my meal take it and continue so maybe u can try that to avoid side effects ..I finished 2 bottles and then the ran out so I was waiting for the restock it’s been a month and now they are bk and I bought two .. my doctor told me gummies aren’t effective because of the process it take to make them the nutrients are lost but in my opinion this works and it’s inexpensive so it’s a win win
